snippet.title: Evolving your story: A guide to AI video editing
snippet.description:
This video explores how to evolve your video narratives with advanced AI editing capabilities using Google Cloud's Veo model. We dive into three powerful features: interpolation for smooth scene transitions, extension for seamlessly lengthening clips, and image guidance for maintaining visual consistency. Discover how Veo gives content creators and developers enhanced creative control, transforming text prompts and images into high-quality, narrative-driven videos.


Chapters:

0:00 - Introduction to AI Video Editing
0:15 - What is Generative Video (Veo)
0:45 - Video Feature 1: Interpolation
2:09 - Video Feature 2: Extension
3:35 - Video Feature 3: Image Guidance
5:04 - Popular Use Cases
5:23 - Conclusion
